
# Goals
##### 1. Inventory system specifically tailored to nurseries and similar models
	a) Tracks items throughout production process (ideally all the way from seed/propagule to marketable product)
	b) Efficiently handles large amounts of loss during production
	c) Easy to input data on new items that have never been handled before
##### 2. Integrated tagging system, compatibility with tagging systems (easy export of data into multiple formats)
##### 3. Integrated info sheet/sales sheet/plant sign generation
##### 4. Compatibility with POS systems (?)

## Desired Features
